title: Statement by the Press Secretary on the Visit of Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu of Israel – The White House
content:
Statements & Releases			

		Foreign Policy	

Issued on:
March 20, 2019
President Donald J. Trump will welcome Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu of Israel to the White House from March 25 to 26, 2019.  The President and the Prime Minister will discuss their countries’ shared interests and actions in the Middle East during a working meeting on March 25.  The President will also host the Prime Minister for dinner on March 26.
